OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMostly cloudy across the region
OL,6,Finitially, but cloud will soon clear
OL,7,Fwestwards to leave a largely fine day
OL,8,Fwith plenty of sunny spells.
OL,9,FTemperatures will be near average,
OL,10,Fthough feeling a little cooler at
OL,11,Ftimes due to the onshore breeze.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FLargely clear at first, but
OL,14,Flow cloud will soon move westwards,
OL,15,Fbringing mostly cloudy conditions by
OL,16,Fdawn. Winds generally falling light
OL,17,Facross the region.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
